How to load the Zotero Pluging:
Step 1: Make sure makefile and zotero-4.0 are in the same directory
Step 2: double click makefile and this will create a file "zotero@chnm.gmu.edu.xpi"
Step 3: drag and drop the .xpi file into firefox 
Note: if drag and drop does not work:
a) Open firefox
b) Ctrl-O
c) browse to the extension and double click the extension (zotero@chnm.gmu.edu.xpi)
d) install the extension
